it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core

Interface Match<A extends Bigraph<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - the kind of bigraph the match belongs.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMatch, AgentMatch, Match, WeightedMatch

    public interface Match<A extends Bigraph<?>>
    This interface describe the basic match of a bigraph in another one. In particular, a match of a bigraph R in G is a triple yielding G when composed. The bigraphs C, R, and P are called Context, Redex and Prameter of the match respectively.
